      "title": "Uthara Sabagaya launched...",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Uthara Sabagaya, a new political alliance, was launched by several parties and former ministers at the Youth Centre in Maharagama. Politicians including Wimal Weerawansa, Udaya Gammanpila, Vasudeva Nanayakakra and Ven. Athureliye Rathana Thera were present at the launch. Pix by Nisal Baduge"
